Ruby/GLib2
==========
Ruby/Glib2 is a Ruby binding of GLib-2.x.

Requirements
------------
   Ruby: http://www.ruby-lang.org/
   GLib: http://www.gtk.org/

Install
-------
   0. install ruby-1.6.x, GLib.
   1. ruby extconf.rb
   2. make
   3. su
   4. make install

